1
00:02:12,220 --> 00:02:15,220
Run for Young

2
00:03:20,220 --> 00:03:24,900
Episode 14 Let's Start Over, Shall We?

3
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:28,920
All right, Jiaojiao, stop looking.

4
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,200
Jiaojiao, let's go.

5
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,760
Prepare for the exam in the afternoon.

6
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:33,200
Maybe Ma Tian is in another

7
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:34,200
exam room, like Anran.

8
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:36,680
His name is on the list of this school.

9
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,480
Ma Tian's grades are so good.

10
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:38,760
He must have handed in the papers early.

11
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:39,520
Have you forgotten?

12
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:41,280
When he transferred here,
he handed in the papers early in the first exam.

13
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:41,880
Yeah.

14
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:45,800
They said that he hadn't showed up.

15
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,640
It's normal.

16
00:03:46,760 --> 00:03:47,600
His grades are so good.

17
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:49,600
It doesn't matter that he took one less subject.

18
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:50,720
Knock it off!

19
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,080
Jiaojiao, go.

20
00:03:52,320 --> 00:03:53,120
Go back to eat.

21
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:54,680
All right, Jiaojiao.

22
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:57,120
May we get out of our misery.

23
00:03:57,320 --> 00:03:58,600
Go for a better future!

24
00:03:58,680 --> 00:03:59,440
Bottoms up.

25
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:00,060
Good!

26
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:01,880
Enjoy it.

27
00:04:01,880 --> 00:04:02,720
Enjoy it.

28
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:05,760
Teammates.

29
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:07,640
Today is a big day.

30
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:09,880
We all should celebrate it.

31
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:10,920
Let's get hammered!

32
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:11,820
Cheers.

33
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:14,160
Doggo.

34
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:25,880
I didn't expect that

35
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:27,640
Ma Tian would skip NCEE.

36
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:32,280
Maybe he did something silly?

37
00:04:32,280 --> 00:04:33,440
Bah, bah, don't talk nonsense!

38
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:35,400
He won't.

39
00:04:35,840 --> 00:04:37,160
Jiaojiao, he won't.

40
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:38,680
Teaty, mind your tongue.

41
00:04:40,960 --> 00:04:42,600
Do you know where Ma Tian is?

42
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,520
I really don't know.

43
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:47,280
Ma Tian's parents are looking for him everywhere.

44
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:50,360
After all, he never let others worry about him.

45
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:53,680
Maybe he is really sad this time.

46
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:59,120
Let's try to find Ma Tian.

47
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:03,800
Right.

48
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:04,720
We're going to find him.

49
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:12,320
But where can you find him?

50
00:05:12,880 --> 00:05:13,720
Chongqing is so big.

51
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:14,840
With so many people.

52
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,560
I don't care.

53
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:17,680
Be it one day or two,

54
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,000
one week,

55
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:20,000
one month, or even a year,

56
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:20,880
I will find him!

57
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:22,960
Jiaojiao.

58
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:59,760
I wonder if Ma Tian can have this.

59
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,360
Have you finished?

60
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,760
We're going to find Ma Tian again.

61
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:07,320
Jiaojiao, we can't look for him

62
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,600
aimlessly.

63
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,480
Then I'll go myself.

64
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,120
This won't work!

65
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:11,880
You'll be exhausted

66
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:13,040
before you find Ma Tian.

67
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:15,080
Do you have a better idea?

68
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:21,000
We can't give up.

69
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:22,440
Jiaojiao.

70
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:24,320
In fact, you should know it very well.

71
00:08:24,960 --> 00:08:26,920
To search for a needle in the haystack is impossible.

72
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:28,640
You're just feeling guilty

73
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:30,520
and punishing yourself.

74
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:33,440
Yes, so it's fine for me to look for him myself.

75
00:08:33,560 --> 00:08:34,520
You're looking for him all day long.

76
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:35,680
You will be exhausted with nothing in return!

77
00:08:35,680 --> 00:08:36,920
- So what shall I do? - It doesn't help!

78
00:08:36,920 --> 00:08:37,840
What if it were Anran?

79
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:38,960
If she disappeared without saying a word,

80
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:39,800
what would you do?

81
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:45,400
Let's go.

82
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:03,760
Good job.

83
00:09:24,520 --> 00:09:25,360
One yuan for each.

84
00:09:53,640 --> 00:09:54,480
Bro.

85
00:09:58,760 --> 00:09:59,920
So you can talk?

86
00:10:04,640 --> 00:10:05,440
I think

87
00:10:06,280 --> 00:10:08,400
you don't look like a wanderer.

88
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,680
Why did you

89
00:10:14,160 --> 00:10:15,320
run away from home?

90
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:19,720
I forgot.

91
00:10:21,400 --> 00:10:22,240
Let me ask you something.

92
00:10:22,920 --> 00:10:23,800
Do you remember

93
00:10:23,800 --> 00:10:26,560
where we sold the scraps yesterday?

94
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:56,720
Hello, who's calling, please?

95
00:11:59,520 --> 00:12:00,320
Hello.

96
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:01,800
Speak.

97
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:04,000
Who is it, please?

98
00:12:05,800 --> 00:12:06,480
Hello.

99
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:07,920
Speak!

100
00:12:08,560 --> 00:12:09,240
Who is that?

101
00:12:10,080 --> 00:12:11,520
Tian, is that you?

102
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:13,680
Hello!

103
00:12:15,040 --> 00:12:15,640
Speak...

104
00:12:28,640 --> 00:12:29,600
Did you guys

105
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:30,720
search the places

106
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:32,240
I asked you to go carefully?

107
00:12:33,040 --> 00:12:34,600
You didn't take this seriously!

108
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:38,000
It's all your fault!

109
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:39,760
You didn't take this seriously at all!

110
00:12:48,760 --> 00:12:49,600
I should have

111
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:51,440
trusted him at first.

112
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:52,840
I should have brought him back that night

113
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:54,200
no matter what.

114
00:12:54,800 --> 00:12:56,120
I should have been by his side

115
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:57,360
when everyone was

116
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,440
talking ill of him.

117
00:13:00,360 --> 00:13:01,920
I knew everything.

118
00:13:01,920 --> 00:13:03,920
But I didn't do anything!

119
00:13:06,040 --> 00:13:08,000
He's out there alone now.

120
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:09,880
He must be suffering

121
00:13:09,880 --> 00:13:12,280
and feeling lonely.

122
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:24,040
Ma Tian.

123
00:13:25,160 --> 00:13:27,160
Where the hell are you?

124
00:13:27,280 --> 00:13:29,160
Where the hell are you!

125
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:32,240
Ma Tian.

126
00:13:33,520 --> 00:13:37,640
Where the hell are you?

127
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:44,720
Where the hell are you!

128
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:10,640
He'll come back.

129
00:14:14,400 --> 00:14:15,640
How do you know?

130
00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:20,320
If not,

131
00:14:20,320 --> 00:14:21,640
my daughter will be exhausted.

132
00:14:21,760 --> 00:14:22,640
What do you mean?

133
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:25,400
As soon as the NCEE is over,

134
00:14:25,680 --> 00:14:27,480
my daughter is looking for him all over Chongqing.

135
00:14:34,880 --> 00:14:35,500
You're back.

136
00:14:36,240 --> 00:14:36,920
Want some noodles?

137
00:14:37,680 --> 00:14:38,360
No appetite.

138
00:14:58,880 --> 00:15:00,120
I'm sure I'll find him.

139
00:15:36,080 --> 00:15:36,960
Why don't you count it?

140
00:15:37,400 --> 00:15:38,060
No need.

141
00:15:39,160 --> 00:15:40,000
How much is it?

142
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:43,960
How much?

143
00:15:44,640 --> 00:15:45,320
What how much?

144
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:47,720
I give you the bottles and you won't pay?

145
00:16:09,520 --> 00:16:10,120
Boss.

146
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:11,440
He came again.

147
00:16:19,880 --> 00:16:20,600
What do you want?

148
00:17:05,240 --> 00:17:06,520
Here, come on.

149
00:17:07,720 --> 00:17:09,040
Go, leave.

150
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:22,760
Hello.

151
00:17:23,600 --> 00:17:24,240
Hello.

152
00:17:25,200 --> 00:17:26,000
Speak.

153
00:17:26,480 --> 00:17:27,120
Who is that?

154
00:17:28,320 --> 00:17:29,600
Dad, I'm back.

155
00:17:30,440 --> 00:17:31,840
Have you heard from Ma Tian?

156
00:17:32,400 --> 00:17:34,120
No. Nothing.

157
00:17:35,520 --> 00:17:37,240
This goddamn Ma Tian!

158
00:17:37,480 --> 00:17:39,400
Don't even know if he is alive or dead now.

159
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:40,080
When I find him,

160
00:17:40,080 --> 00:17:41,200
I'll break his leg!

161
00:17:42,960 --> 00:17:44,120
Unlucky child!

162
00:18:02,600 --> 00:18:03,439
Jiaojiao.

163
00:18:03,439 --> 00:18:04,439
Where are you going so early?

164
00:18:04,919 --> 00:18:05,880
Go find Ma Tian.

165
00:18:06,240 --> 00:18:06,880
Wait a minute.

166
00:18:07,480 --> 00:18:08,120
Why don't you

167
00:18:08,120 --> 00:18:09,240
wait for us to go together?

168
00:18:09,480 --> 00:18:10,480
Take some rest.

169
00:18:10,480 --> 00:18:11,240
I'll go by myself.

170
00:18:11,240 --> 00:18:11,880
No.

171
00:18:12,280 --> 00:18:13,280
Look at your dark circles.

172
00:18:13,320 --> 00:18:14,200
You need more rest.

173
00:18:14,600 --> 00:18:15,480
There is no news of him.

174
00:18:15,480 --> 00:18:17,000
I can't rest well.

175
00:18:17,120 --> 00:18:17,960
We'll go with you.

176
00:18:18,160 --> 00:18:19,040
You guys have a rest.

177
00:18:19,040 --> 00:18:19,640
I'll go with you.

178
00:18:19,840 --> 00:18:20,760
Luo Shenxi.

179
00:18:22,680 --> 00:18:24,040
I knew you didn't want to go.

180
00:18:26,520 --> 00:18:27,160
Who is she?

181
00:18:29,040 --> 00:18:29,760
Coco.

182
00:18:32,280 --> 00:18:32,880
You...

183
00:18:33,560 --> 00:18:34,360
Why are you here?

184
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:45,560
Why did you bring my notice for missing person?

185
00:18:46,280 --> 00:18:48,560
Is he your friend?

186
00:18:52,560 --> 00:18:54,360
When did you make this?

187
00:18:55,440 --> 00:18:56,560
I printed some before

188
00:18:56,560 --> 00:18:57,440
and posted it.

189
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:01,520
Thank you, Big Mouth.

190
00:19:03,480 --> 00:19:04,400
You are here to tell us

191
00:19:04,400 --> 00:19:05,480
you know where Ma Tian is?

192
00:19:05,480 --> 00:19:06,100
Right.

193
00:19:09,320 --> 00:19:10,080
I'm sorry.

194
00:19:14,280 --> 00:19:15,120
Actually,

195
00:19:16,040 --> 00:19:17,480
here is the thing.

196
00:19:21,240 --> 00:19:21,880
Jiaojiao.

197
00:19:23,880 --> 00:19:24,760
I'm sorry.

198
00:19:27,480 --> 00:19:28,720
Why apologize?

199
00:19:30,600 --> 00:19:31,880
It was Coco who set up Ma Tian.

200
00:19:33,320 --> 00:19:34,520
I feel guilty, too.

201
00:19:37,360 --> 00:19:38,560
None of your business.

202
00:19:43,320 --> 00:19:44,000
I will find a way

203
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:45,160
to get Ma Tian back.

204
00:19:53,680 --> 00:19:56,360
Now that you know these things,

205
00:19:57,360 --> 00:19:58,600
do you still like Coco?

206
00:20:03,360 --> 00:20:04,520
Do you think that

207
00:20:05,280 --> 00:20:06,480
I'm very unpromising.

208
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:07,600
No.

209
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:09,000
Why?

210
00:20:10,200 --> 00:20:11,920
There's nothing wrong with falling for someone.

211
00:20:12,840 --> 00:20:14,680
And she came to confess it.

212
00:20:14,680 --> 00:20:15,800
It's no big deal.

213
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:18,560
Don't worry.

214
00:20:19,240 --> 00:20:21,240
I won't tell anyone about it.

215
00:20:25,760 --> 00:20:26,360
Let's go.

216
00:20:27,640 --> 00:20:28,840
I'll go with you

217
00:20:29,200 --> 00:20:30,440
to find your beloved one.

218
00:20:31,800 --> 00:20:32,400
Hey, boy.

219
00:20:33,680 --> 00:20:34,300
Get up.

220
00:20:35,760 --> 00:20:36,380
Quickly.

221
00:20:39,080 --> 00:20:39,720
Give me your money.

222
00:20:41,160 --> 00:20:41,920
What are you looking at?

223
00:20:41,920 --> 00:20:42,960
Give me the money!

224
00:20:48,960 --> 00:20:50,040
Come on. Quick.

225
00:20:52,440 --> 00:20:53,060
Get him!

226
00:20:53,360 --> 00:20:54,520
Stop there!

227
00:20:55,040 --> 00:20:55,660
Don't you run!

228
00:20:57,520 --> 00:20:58,160
Stop!

229
00:21:00,560 --> 00:21:01,600
Why are you running away?

230
00:21:02,080 --> 00:21:02,840
Give us the money!

231
00:21:03,800 --> 00:21:04,560
Do you hear me?

232
00:21:09,200 --> 00:21:09,920
Give me or not?

233
00:21:16,480 --> 00:21:17,800
Then what shall I buy food with these days?

234
00:21:17,800 --> 00:21:19,320
I don't give a damn.

235
00:21:21,160 --> 00:21:22,000
Is that all?

236
00:21:22,520 --> 00:21:23,320
That's all I have.

237
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:24,560
What about them?

238
00:21:28,440 --> 00:21:29,240
Who are you?

239
00:21:30,160 --> 00:21:31,040
None of your business.

240
00:21:32,640 --> 00:21:33,680
Give him the money back!

241
00:21:34,520 --> 00:21:35,440
Why should I?

242
00:21:38,080 --> 00:21:38,960
Believe it or not,

243
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:41,440
I'll call the police.

244
00:21:44,240 --> 00:21:45,000
Call the police?

245
00:21:45,640 --> 00:21:47,120
He is a fool!

246
00:21:47,120 --> 00:21:48,040
Go call the police.

247
00:21:48,040 --> 00:21:49,000
Call the police!

248
00:21:49,040 --> 00:21:50,000
What are you going to do?

249
00:21:50,240 --> 00:21:51,640
Just call the police.

250
00:21:53,080 --> 00:21:54,160
I feel pain in my head.

251
00:21:55,200 --> 00:21:56,760
If you break my head, you will pay for it.

252
00:21:58,880 --> 00:22:00,240
Weren't you so cocky just now?

253
00:22:00,720 --> 00:22:01,480
Playing cool, huh?

254
00:22:02,320 --> 00:22:04,160
Don't show up in front of me again.

255
00:22:05,600 --> 00:22:06,240
Go, go.

256
00:22:06,760 --> 00:22:07,480
Don't look back.

257
00:22:08,360 --> 00:22:09,040
There are many of them.

258
00:22:09,160 --> 00:22:10,200
All desperadoes.

259
00:22:10,320 --> 00:22:11,240
They didn't catch up, did they?

260
00:22:15,320 --> 00:22:15,940
Run!

261
00:22:16,840 --> 00:22:17,440
Go!

262
00:22:18,040 --> 00:22:18,640
Idiots, stop!

263
00:22:23,160 --> 00:22:24,000
Stop there!

264
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:24,640
Don't run.

265
00:22:36,840 --> 00:22:37,760
Is my head okay?

266
00:22:39,560 --> 00:22:40,680
It's just a little red.

267
00:22:47,840 --> 00:22:48,880
To survive in society,

268
00:22:49,640 --> 00:22:50,640
I rely on my tough head.

269
00:22:52,200 --> 00:22:53,160
Don't tell anyone.

270
00:22:57,400 --> 00:22:58,800
How did you become like this?

271
00:22:59,480 --> 00:23:00,480
You have changed so much.

272
00:23:01,840 --> 00:23:03,320
And how did you become like this?

273
00:23:04,920 --> 00:23:05,960
Why did you come to Chengdu?

274
00:23:07,480 --> 00:23:08,760
Why are you in Chengdu, too?

275
00:23:10,320 --> 00:23:11,760
I open a noodle restaurant in Chengdu.

276
00:23:12,360 --> 00:23:13,200
Do some business.

277
00:23:15,400 --> 00:23:16,560
You look like a beggar.

278
00:23:17,840 --> 00:23:18,460
Go.

279
00:23:22,200 --> 00:23:23,160
Miss, pea paste noodles.

280
00:23:23,160 --> 00:23:25,440
OK, pea paste noodles. Coming.

281
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:28,120
Liu's Chongqing Noodles

282
00:23:35,280 --> 00:23:36,000
I'm back.

283
00:23:36,320 --> 00:23:36,940
You're back.

284
00:23:37,840 --> 00:23:38,560
OK.

285
00:23:40,600 --> 00:23:41,440
Come in.

286
00:23:50,840 --> 00:23:51,560
You own it?

287
00:23:53,400 --> 00:23:54,520
Me and my girlfriend.

288
00:24:11,160 --> 00:24:12,160
Your girlfriend?

289
00:24:15,320 --> 00:24:16,000
We'll marry

290
00:24:16,200 --> 00:24:16,880
in two years.

291
00:24:20,080 --> 00:24:20,680
Xin.

292
00:24:21,000 --> 00:24:21,720
A bowl of noodles.

293
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:23,080
OK.

294
00:24:29,560 --> 00:24:30,560
I haven't seen you for months.

295
00:24:32,320 --> 00:24:33,360
Why are you a beggar

296
00:24:33,360 --> 00:24:34,280
instead of a student?

297
00:24:37,280 --> 00:24:37,880
I graduated.

298
00:24:38,560 --> 00:24:39,680
You graduated

299
00:24:41,840 --> 00:24:42,920
and became a beggar?

300
00:24:42,920 --> 00:24:44,160
This starting point is low.

301
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:49,880
What happened?

302
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:53,760
Nothing.

303
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:56,120
Forget it if you don't want to say it.

304
00:24:57,600 --> 00:24:58,520
Before you go back,

305
00:24:58,520 --> 00:24:59,280
stay at my place.

306
00:25:06,120 --> 00:25:07,480
At least, you'll have food.

307
00:25:07,680 --> 00:25:08,960
Do you really want to be a beggar?

308
00:25:10,520 --> 00:25:12,520
Help us in the shop.

309
00:25:13,640 --> 00:25:14,320
Or

310
00:25:14,800 --> 00:25:16,480
I'll introduce you to work in a bar?

311
00:25:19,280 --> 00:25:19,920
It's the same.

312
00:25:20,360 --> 00:25:21,040
Whatever.

313
00:25:21,840 --> 00:25:22,680
The other day,

314
00:25:23,200 --> 00:25:24,520
I got a call.

315
00:25:25,400 --> 00:25:26,600
I picked it up

316
00:25:27,520 --> 00:25:29,240
but no one talked.

317
00:25:30,320 --> 00:25:32,680
I didn't think much about it at that time.

318
00:25:33,880 --> 00:25:35,040
But these days,

319
00:25:36,880 --> 00:25:38,280
I felt like

320
00:25:39,800 --> 00:25:41,000
it must be Ma Tian.

321
00:25:41,320 --> 00:25:42,960
I also received a phone call two days ago.

322
00:25:43,720 --> 00:25:45,280
I asked who that was, but no one talked.

323
00:25:45,840 --> 00:25:46,880
Maybe it was also him.

324
00:25:47,760 --> 00:25:50,520
Dad, why didn't you tell me!

325
00:25:50,600 --> 00:25:51,360
I didn't?

326
00:25:51,440 --> 00:25:54,000
You didn't tell me such important news.

327
00:25:54,200 --> 00:25:55,000
He didn't talk...

328
00:25:55,280 --> 00:25:56,040
It's all your fault!

329
00:25:56,040 --> 00:25:58,200
I called back this morning and asked.

330
00:25:58,680 --> 00:26:01,080
It is a public telephone in a grocery in Chengdu.

331
00:26:01,720 --> 00:26:03,640
By the way, I wrote down the address.

332
00:26:05,520 --> 00:26:06,120
Look.

333
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:07,960
No matter what,

334
00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:09,320
let's go to Chengdu tomorrow.

335
00:26:10,800 --> 00:26:11,440
OK.

336
00:26:24,440 --> 00:26:26,520
Prince Melancholy pretends to be melancholy again.

337
00:26:28,560 --> 00:26:29,200
Come on.

338
00:26:38,360 --> 00:26:39,000
Say it.

339
00:26:39,400 --> 00:26:40,480
What the hell happened?

340
00:26:45,200 --> 00:26:45,840
I'm wronged.

341
00:26:49,240 --> 00:26:50,720
You think everyone should

342
00:26:50,720 --> 00:26:51,800
trust you unconditionally?

343
00:26:53,840 --> 00:26:54,600
That's not true.

344
00:26:55,720 --> 00:26:57,280
At least my relatives

345
00:26:57,720 --> 00:26:58,600
and the one I care about the most

346
00:26:58,680 --> 00:27:00,040
should believe me unconditionally.

347
00:27:04,080 --> 00:27:04,800
Right.

348
00:27:09,800 --> 00:27:10,600
What is it?

349
00:27:12,560 --> 00:27:14,200
I thought you would try to persuade me

350
00:27:14,200 --> 00:27:15,360
and defend for them.

351
00:27:17,440 --> 00:27:18,720
No one should ask

352
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:20,680
a heart-broken man to be magnanimous.

353
00:27:22,440 --> 00:27:24,840
But leaving without saying anything

354
00:27:25,400 --> 00:27:27,000
isn't a good solution.

355
00:27:29,800 --> 00:27:30,600
I tried.

356
00:27:48,600 --> 00:27:49,440
What is this?

357
00:27:51,240 --> 00:27:51,840
Lottery.

358
00:27:52,840 --> 00:27:54,040
I buy one every day.

359
00:27:55,120 --> 00:27:55,880
You are so unlucky.

360
00:27:56,720 --> 00:27:58,120
Maybe you will bring me good luck.

361
00:27:58,120 --> 00:27:59,000
How much can you win?

362
00:27:59,200 --> 00:27:59,880
Fifty.

363
00:28:00,600 --> 00:28:01,640
Only fifty?

364
00:28:09,120 --> 00:28:09,760
I won.

365
00:28:11,960 --> 00:28:12,560
I won!

366
00:28:15,360 --> 00:28:16,080
I won!

367
00:28:16,640 --> 00:28:18,200
I won!

368
00:28:18,320 --> 00:28:19,120
I won.

369
00:28:19,880 --> 00:28:20,480
I won.

370
00:28:20,680 --> 00:28:21,400
I won.

371
00:28:22,760 --> 00:28:24,840
It's only 50. Come on!

372
00:28:41,800 --> 00:28:42,440
Hercules Jiao.

373
00:28:43,100 --> 00:28:43,720
We can't keep

374
00:28:43,720 --> 00:28:44,960
looking for him like this.

375
00:28:45,360 --> 00:28:46,520
We don't know if Ma Tian will

376
00:28:46,520 --> 00:28:47,680
go back to the grocery.

377
00:28:50,560 --> 00:28:52,360
We can't go on like this.

378
00:28:52,880 --> 00:28:55,240
I have to contact the local police,

379
00:28:55,720 --> 00:28:57,520
newspapers, TV stations and so on.

380
00:29:00,240 --> 00:29:01,440
Let's keep looking.

381
00:29:01,440 --> 00:29:03,920
We just need to sit in the car and go to a few more places.

382
00:29:12,000 --> 00:29:13,240
Why are you here alone?

383
00:29:13,320 --> 00:29:13,960
Where's Qin?

384
00:29:15,200 --> 00:29:15,800
There.

385
00:29:17,520 --> 00:29:18,240
What is he doing?

386
00:29:19,880 --> 00:29:21,400
He's looking for the lottery

387
00:29:21,920 --> 00:29:22,600
bought in the morning.

388
00:29:23,880 --> 00:29:24,680
Fifty yuan.

389
00:29:26,480 --> 00:29:27,560
Fifty yuan.

390
00:29:28,600 --> 00:29:30,720
I'm feel embarrassed.

391
00:29:31,640 --> 00:29:34,600
What kind of man would check the trash can

392
00:29:34,600 --> 00:29:37,080
in the middle of the night just for a lottery ticket?

393
00:29:38,840 --> 00:29:40,640
Though he's like this now,

394
00:29:40,960 --> 00:29:42,960
he used to be so cool

395
00:29:42,960 --> 00:29:44,080
that all girls liked him.

396
00:29:45,520 --> 00:29:47,000
Seriously?

397
00:29:47,000 --> 00:29:47,960
Don't lie.

398
00:29:48,280 --> 00:29:49,440
Haven't you heard of Li Anran?

399
00:29:52,640 --> 00:29:53,880
Li Anran?

400
00:29:55,040 --> 00:29:56,520
I'll help Qin.

401
00:29:58,960 --> 00:29:59,880
Qin, let's go home.

402
00:30:00,960 --> 00:30:01,680
Leave me alone.

403
00:30:02,080 --> 00:30:03,840
It's just fifty. Come on.

404
00:30:03,960 --> 00:30:04,920
Stop it.

405
00:30:05,000 --> 00:30:05,600
Get lost.

406
00:30:13,280 --> 00:30:14,680
How about I give you 50?

407
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:21,640
It's not about the money.

408
00:30:21,800 --> 00:30:22,760
What's that about?

409
00:30:32,160 --> 00:30:34,000
That is my first good luck.

410
00:30:34,760 --> 00:30:36,280
And it passed away!

411
00:30:43,000 --> 00:30:44,280
Help me find it.

412
00:31:00,800 --> 00:31:01,480
Qin.

413
00:31:02,120 --> 00:31:03,480
Life is long.

414
00:31:27,920 --> 00:31:29,040
Stop looking.

415
00:31:29,880 --> 00:31:30,840
What are you looking for?

416
00:31:32,560 --> 00:31:34,160
This is my fate!

417
00:32:30,680 --> 00:32:31,280
Jiaojiao.

418
00:32:34,360 --> 00:32:35,600
Jiaojiao, you are still awake?

419
00:32:45,600 --> 00:32:46,520
Rest assured.

420
00:32:46,960 --> 00:32:48,160
I'm sure we can find him.

421
00:32:50,000 --> 00:32:50,920
Go to sleep.

422
00:33:54,400 --> 00:33:55,160
Ma Tian!

423
00:34:07,080 --> 00:34:07,880
Tian!

424
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:09,960
Tian!

425
00:34:10,360 --> 00:34:11,080
Tian!

426
00:34:12,440 --> 00:34:13,680
Tian, it is really you!

427
00:34:17,360 --> 00:34:18,200
Tian.

428
00:34:22,360 --> 00:34:22,980
Tian.

429
00:34:24,200 --> 00:34:25,880
I finally found you!

430
00:34:27,600 --> 00:34:28,220
Tian.

431
00:34:29,800 --> 00:34:30,800
I'm glad you're okay.

432
00:34:31,280 --> 00:34:32,120
Let's go.

433
00:34:32,280 --> 00:34:33,040
Go home with me.

434
00:34:33,080 --> 00:34:33,720
Quickly.

435
00:34:38,600 --> 00:34:39,220
Yes.

436
00:34:40,440 --> 00:34:41,060
Yes.

437
00:34:41,960 --> 00:34:44,280
We know the whole story.

438
00:34:46,080 --> 00:34:48,040
We misunderstood you.

439
00:34:49,120 --> 00:34:50,040
Why?

440
00:34:52,040 --> 00:34:52,719
At that time,

441
00:34:55,360 --> 00:34:56,640
we were very angry.

442
00:34:58,360 --> 00:35:00,360
It happened suddenly, so...

443
00:35:01,040 --> 00:35:01,640
Mom.

444
00:35:04,440 --> 00:35:05,520
I am disappointed

445
00:35:07,279 --> 00:35:07,880
because sometimes

446
00:35:07,880 --> 00:35:10,120
you just can't prove your innocence.

447
00:35:12,680 --> 00:35:13,319
But there are people

448
00:35:13,319 --> 00:35:14,799
you don't have to prove yourself to them,

449
00:35:16,000 --> 00:35:17,319
and they will embrace you

450
00:35:17,319 --> 00:35:18,840
no matter what others say.

451
00:35:24,799 --> 00:35:26,480
But as my parents, you didn't.

452
00:35:31,680 --> 00:35:32,319
Son.

453
00:35:33,600 --> 00:35:34,719
I'm sorry.

454
00:35:35,640 --> 00:35:36,640
Please go back.

455
00:35:36,960 --> 00:35:38,360
I can't rest assured.

456
00:35:38,360 --> 00:35:39,520
I'm not going back.

457
00:35:40,800 --> 00:35:42,120
Wait till I feel better.

458
00:35:43,560 --> 00:35:44,160
I...

459
00:35:44,240 --> 00:35:44,860
No.

460
00:35:45,160 --> 00:35:45,800
Son.

461
00:35:50,800 --> 00:35:52,360
Let me help you.

462
00:35:53,240 --> 00:35:53,840
Son.

463
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:58,720
What happened?

464
00:36:06,480 --> 00:36:07,680
Tian, I was wrong.

465
00:36:07,680 --> 00:36:09,080
Come home with me, OK?

466
00:36:10,640 --> 00:36:11,800
It was my fault.

467
00:36:12,440 --> 00:36:13,720
Tian, go home with me!

468
00:36:13,720 --> 00:36:14,600
Listen to me.

469
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:20,600
Tian.

470
00:36:48,640 --> 00:36:49,520
Liu Wenqin.

471
00:36:51,960 --> 00:36:52,880
It's been a while.

472
00:37:03,720 --> 00:37:04,520
Qin.

473
00:37:07,120 --> 00:37:07,760
Long time no see.

474
00:37:08,400 --> 00:37:09,040
Long time no see.

475
00:37:09,440 --> 00:37:10,800
Qin, why are you here?

476
00:37:11,800 --> 00:37:12,480
I own a noodle shop.

477
00:37:14,280 --> 00:37:14,920
You own it?

478
00:37:15,240 --> 00:37:16,640
You really opened a noodle shop!

479
00:37:18,480 --> 00:37:19,320
What?

480
00:37:19,320 --> 00:37:20,360
We haven't met for long.

481
00:37:22,440 --> 00:37:23,360
How are you doing?

482
00:37:24,600 --> 00:37:25,920
Of course I'm doing well.

483
00:37:26,240 --> 00:37:27,320
I took the NCEE.

484
00:37:27,320 --> 00:37:28,640
I may be a college student!

485
00:37:29,040 --> 00:37:30,000
Hard to tell.

486
00:37:30,440 --> 00:37:31,880
There is hope.

487
00:37:34,160 --> 00:37:35,840
Thanks to Anran who helped me with my study.

488
00:37:35,840 --> 00:37:37,600
Otherwise, I can't go to college.

489
00:37:42,720 --> 00:37:44,360
My girlfriend, Li Xin.

490
00:37:47,040 --> 00:37:47,840
Your girlfriend?

491
00:37:51,840 --> 00:37:52,440
Your friends?

492
00:37:59,040 --> 00:37:59,700
Li Anran.

493
00:38:00,720 --> 00:38:01,360
Hello.

494
00:38:01,560 --> 00:38:02,600
I'm Qin's girlfriend.

495
00:38:02,600 --> 00:38:03,200
I'm Li Xin.

496
00:38:03,320 --> 00:38:04,120
Hello, Xin.

497
00:38:06,160 --> 00:38:06,760
He's Doggo.

498
00:38:07,760 --> 00:38:08,360
Hello, Xin.

499
00:38:08,840 --> 00:38:09,920
Just call me Doggo.

500
00:38:10,000 --> 00:38:10,840
Hello, Doggo.

501
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:21,320
Qin.

502
00:38:23,480 --> 00:38:24,560
All right, I'm telling you.

503
00:38:24,560 --> 00:38:25,520
Qin owns a noodle shop.

504
00:38:25,640 --> 00:38:26,880
Qin owns a noodle shop now?

505
00:38:26,880 --> 00:38:27,680
Boss Liu!

506
00:38:27,680 --> 00:38:28,480
Boss Liu.

507
00:38:29,400 --> 00:38:30,320
You come for Ma Tian together?

508
00:38:33,240 --> 00:38:33,860
Aunt.

509
00:38:35,880 --> 00:38:36,840
Don't worry.

510
00:38:37,720 --> 00:38:38,960
I'll take care of Ma Tian.

511
00:38:39,440 --> 00:38:40,520
Don't be sad.

512
00:38:41,720 --> 00:38:43,000
I'll try to persuade him later.

513
00:38:43,000 --> 00:38:43,960
If you force him now,

514
00:38:43,960 --> 00:38:45,600
he might do something worse.

515
00:38:45,880 --> 00:38:47,520
I was like that before.

516
00:38:47,520 --> 00:38:48,760
I am also from Chongqing.

517
00:38:48,760 --> 00:38:49,960
I'll definitely bring him back.

518
00:38:58,080 --> 00:38:59,560
He is too stubborn.

519
00:38:59,880 --> 00:39:00,920
Give him some time.

520
00:39:02,920 --> 00:39:03,520
Thank you.

521
00:39:03,760 --> 00:39:04,840
It's okay. No worries.

522
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:06,920
Take care of yourself, aunt.

523
00:39:13,480 --> 00:39:14,120
Jiaojiao.

524
00:39:15,400 --> 00:39:16,120
It's fine.

525
00:39:19,400 --> 00:39:20,240
I'll get back to work.

526
00:39:20,520 --> 00:39:21,680
- OK. - You see them off.

527
00:39:23,840 --> 00:39:24,880
Rest assured.

528
00:39:26,040 --> 00:39:27,160
I'm sorry, Qin.

529
00:39:27,480 --> 00:39:29,480
Ma Tian has been acting up.

530
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:31,000
We're afraid he may run away.

531
00:39:31,360 --> 00:39:32,200
We'd better leave.

532
00:39:32,200 --> 00:39:33,240
Yes.

533
00:39:34,200 --> 00:39:35,560
Before you go to college,

534
00:39:35,560 --> 00:39:36,840
come to Chengdu and have fun.

535
00:39:36,840 --> 00:39:39,000
You may not have time after you go to college.

536
00:39:39,160 --> 00:39:39,760
All right.

537
00:39:47,360 --> 00:39:47,960
Bye.

538
00:39:52,400 --> 00:39:53,680
Bye, Qin.

539
00:39:54,080 --> 00:39:54,880
See you around.

540
00:40:02,080 --> 00:40:02,760
Qin.

541
00:40:07,480 --> 00:40:08,640
Xin is very beautiful.

542
00:40:09,480 --> 00:40:10,520
Wish you happy.

543
00:40:16,720 --> 00:40:17,400
Oh.

544
00:40:17,400 --> 00:40:18,160
Wish you and Doggo

545
00:40:21,120 --> 00:40:21,920
happy, too.

546
00:40:45,640 --> 00:40:46,280
Stop.

547
00:40:47,600 --> 00:40:48,360
What?

548
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:51,320
I've been looking for him everywhere.

549
00:40:51,320 --> 00:40:52,400
I can't just go back like this.

550
00:40:52,400 --> 00:40:53,000
Jiaojiao.

551
00:40:53,080 --> 00:40:53,720
All right, Jiaojiao.

552
00:40:53,720 --> 00:40:55,160
We now know where Ma Tian is

553
00:40:55,160 --> 00:40:56,080
and how he is doing.

554
00:40:56,080 --> 00:40:57,520
Let's come pick him up after he calms down.

555
00:40:57,520 --> 00:40:58,160
Yeah.

556
00:40:58,160 --> 00:40:59,200
- Jiaojiao. - Stop!

557
00:41:00,720 --> 00:41:01,760
Jiaojiao!

558
00:41:01,760 --> 00:41:02,920
I'll stay with him.

559
00:41:02,920 --> 00:41:04,800
I won't let him leave me this time.

560
00:41:05,040 --> 00:41:05,640
No!

561
00:41:05,880 --> 00:41:06,920
Jiaojiao!

562
00:41:06,920 --> 00:41:08,560
Why are you so willful?

563
00:41:08,560 --> 00:41:09,160
Jiaojiao.

564
00:41:09,360 --> 00:41:10,040
Jiaojiao.

565
00:41:10,200 --> 00:41:10,920
Forget it, aunt.

566
00:41:11,960 --> 00:41:13,840
She is stubborn as a rock.

567
00:41:14,960 --> 00:41:15,720
This girl...

568
00:41:16,480 --> 00:41:17,680
If we let her go...

569
00:41:18,640 --> 00:41:19,920
I know her.

570
00:41:20,280 --> 00:41:21,920
Even if we get her back to Chongqing,

571
00:41:22,280 --> 00:41:23,960
she will come here herself.

572
00:41:38,960 --> 00:41:39,840
I'm back again.

573
00:41:45,280 --> 00:41:48,000
You should sit like this when eating noodles.

574
00:41:50,160 --> 00:41:51,120
Do you know that?

575
00:41:51,120 --> 00:41:52,760
You have to step on the chair like this.

576
00:41:52,840 --> 00:41:54,840
Like this, shake your legs

577
00:41:54,840 --> 00:41:56,280
while eating.

578
00:41:56,280 --> 00:41:57,680
Put your feet like this.

579
00:41:58,980 --> 00:41:59,600
Did you forget?

580
00:41:59,600 --> 00:42:01,320
Eat while shaking your feet like this.

581
00:42:01,680 --> 00:42:02,680
Eat while shaking.

582
00:42:02,680 --> 00:42:04,000
Shake your feet.

583
00:42:04,800 --> 00:42:07,160
I taught you to shake and eat like this before.

584
00:42:23,160 --> 00:42:23,960
Ma Tian!

585
00:42:26,440 --> 00:42:27,640
You've mistaken me for someone else.

586
00:42:29,880 --> 00:42:31,080
Then who are you?

587
00:42:35,640 --> 00:42:36,800
I'm Li Yaohui.

588
00:42:37,520 --> 00:42:38,640
Li Yaohui?

589
00:42:39,960 --> 00:42:41,320
Seriously?

590
00:43:10,080 --> 00:43:12,400
Hello, I'm He Baorong.

591
00:43:17,360 --> 00:43:20,080
Let's start over, shall we?
